63. find a solution to a system of equations
      Returns a solution to a system of equations.
      Syntax: x = solvep({Equations},{Variables})
      Allowed types for x: qubit, cbit, qnum, qnump, cnum, qstr, qstrs, qstrc, qstre, cstr, ctrs, ctrc, cstre, matrix, block, circ, list, dict, set, map. 
